  <brief_title>Randomized Clinical Trial for Primary Molar Pulpotomy, Biodentine Vs Formocresol-ZOE</brief_title>
  <official_title>A New Technique for Primary Molar Pulpotomy : A Randomized Clinical Trial Comparing the Radiographic and Clinical Success of the Formocresol-zinc Oxide Eugenol Technique and the Biodentine Technique</official_title>
